      <title>洛杉矶山火导致爱迪生国际股票和债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/southern-california-edison-bonds-widen-amid-wildfires-in-la-area</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，一场山火肆虐洛杉矶地区，靠近爱迪生国际公用事业部门所服务的地区，导致爱迪生国际的股价和债券下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/southern-california-edison-bonds-widen-amid-wildfires-in-la-area</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 17:29:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市动荡，华尔街为就业报告做好准备：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员不愿进行高风险押注，股市难以获得支撑，周五就业报告出炉前市场即将收盘。美国国债在 220 亿美元的稳健抛售中企稳，在近期收益率飙升后，这在一定程度上缓解了市场压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 22:33:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
